Development Roadmap for 1.2.x
-----------------------------
Version: $Id$

C = Committed

1.2.9
C       #1532 - Human readable disk free
        #1711 - IPv6 support
C       #1828 - mod_sql can only find mysql.sock if in /tmp
C       #1849 - Compile can have trouble finding mysql.h
C       #1869 - Add option to ftpwho/ftpcount/ftptop
C       #1915 - Unsafe pointer usage in scoreboard file format 
C       #1921 - Socket-level performance tweaks
C       #1932 - Make Max* checks a PASS POST_CMD handler
C       #1933 - Add mod_ifsession contrib module
C       #1960 - Add removed file size by DELE command to xferlog
C       #1967 - Add display of uptime to ftpwho, ftptop
C       Add RootRevoke, AnonRejectPasswords directives

1.2.10

        #1925 - Clean up of Class code
        #1696 - Include directive supports directories
        #1965 - Changing timing of handling of QUIT command
        #2013 - Track RFC2228 sessions in scoreboard
        #2015 - Add AND, OR keywords to Allow/Deny User/Group directives
        #2052 - ProFTPD "ununsed parameters" cleanup
        #2062 - Enhance UserOwner/GroupOwner to take IDs as well as name
                parameters
        #2072 - Add Controls API
        #2086 - Add limits for PORT, PASV
        #2098 - Add SetEnv, UnsetEnv directives
        #2105 - Remove *Authoritative directives
	#2107 - Fix handling of $Libraries$ tag, --with-libraries option

